Date:  1/10/2005
Source:  Dominion Post
Author:
Vol / Page:  E13
Edition:
Quote:  They are by any standard exceptional trees, but the hero of our story, who goes by the name of makamaka, is also exceptional. ... Makamaka, with the botanic name of <i>Ackama rosifolia</i>, has leaves similar to those of a rose bush, having paired leaflets along the central midrib with a single leaflet at the leaf tip.
